---
title: Double Salt & Pepper Chicken with Garlic Rice, Honey-Soy Veggies & Mayo
description: Watch out salt and pepper squid, because our chicken version is going to steal even your biggest fans! With all the spicy flavour, but pan-fried instead of deep-fried, this is a quick and easy dinner that's going to blow your mind.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66be8ab43546b43b79d2ec5c-67105b84.jpeg
